    "description": "Are you a skilled Senior Software Engineer looking for your next big career move? Mindtree Asia Pacific Associates in Allahabad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Mindtree Asia Pacific Associates:\nMindtree Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mindtree Asia Pacific Associates!",
